### Runtime Round 60 - Full E2E regression / inner test readiness
# Scope: Resource -> Schema -> Metadata -> Validation -> Publish -> References -> TestRun -> Trace -> Runtime hardening.
# Command:
#   npx tsx scripts/verify-microflow-round60-full-e2e.ts
# Evidence:
#   artifacts/microflow-e2e/round60/e2e-summary.json
#   artifacts/microflow-e2e/round60/e2e-summary.md
#   artifacts/microflow-e2e/round60/failed-cases.json
#   artifacts/microflow-e2e/round60/coverage-matrix.json
# Safety:
# - Round60 seed/reset only deletes names starting with R60_E2E_ or E2E_MF_.
# - Requests below use AuthoringSchema only; FlowGram JSON must not be persisted.

### Round 60 - Health / Environment
# Expected JSON path:
# - $.success=true
# - $.data.status="ok"
GET {{host}}/api/microflows/health
X-Workspace-Id: {{workspaceId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}

